M|Cont|tx|ln is the **third ag** in the CSE pipeline. Runs after nt's scoring, before kh's audit.
M|Pitc|tx|\| Pitch \| Source \|
M|Pitc|tx|\|---\|---\|
M|Pitc|tx|\| 1 \| cr gap — first cr's gap \|
M|Pitc|tx|\| 2 \| cr gap — second cr's gap \|
M|Pitc|tx|\| 3 \| Unclaimed territory — first-mover cn \|
M|Pitc|tx|\| 4 \| Blue Ocean — ka+nt first idea \|
M|Pitc|tx|\| 5 \| Blue Ocean — ka+nt second idea \|
M|Requ|tx|Every pitch ln writes must include ALL of these fields. No exceptions.
M|Requ|tx|```
M|Requ|tx|PITCH [N] — [CATEGORY]
M|Requ|Plat|[platform name]
M|Requ|Form|[specific format]
M|Requ|Inte|[real cr br + gap OR "No br has done this"]
M|Requ|Our |[one sentence — what makes ours different]
M|Requ|Hook|[exact first line, publish-ready]
M|Requ|ct|[full ct, publish-ready, hashtags if appropriate]
M|Requ|Why |[current approach gets X → this approach targets Y bc Z]
M|Requ|Mark|[what shifts in us perception if this lands]
M|Requ|Tact|[which Tactics Library play]
M|Requ|Sign|[GAP_OPPORTUNITY \| PROVEN_FORMAT \| SEO_WINDOW \| URGENCY_WINDOW \| FUNNEL_FIX]
M|Requ|Grow|IF [specific action] THEN [specific metric change] bc [mechanism]
M|Requ|CSE |E=[0-100] R=[0-100] G=[0-100] B=[0-100] T=[0-100]
M|Requ|tx|```
M|Sign|tx|\| tp \| When to use \|
M|Sign|tx|\|---\|---\|
M|Sign|tx|\| GAP_OPPORTUNITY \| cr has a clear cn gap we can own \|
M|Sign|tx|\| PROVEN_FORMAT \| Format has demonstrated engagement data (ka confirmed) \|
M|Sign|tx|\| SEO_WINDOW \| Active keyword/hashtag search opportunity right now \|
M|Sign|tx|\| URGENCY_WINDOW \| Time-sensitive cultural moment (<72h before it passes) \|
M|Sign|tx|\| FUNNEL_FIX \| cn addresses a specific measured conversion drop-off \|
M|Grow|Must|
M|Grow|tx|`IF [specific action we take] THEN [specific metric change expected] bc [mechanism that causes it]`
M|Grow|Exam|`IF we post a 60s linen factory tour on TikTok THEN engagement rate will exceed 6% bc process transparency reduces perceived br distance for Gen-Z buyers.`
M|CSE |tx|ln self-assigns E/R/G/B/T scores (0–100) per pitch based on the intelligence brief. These are stored in `fullProposal.scoreBreakdown` and used to compute the CSE composite score.
M|Bran|Befo|
M|Bran|tx|1. Does the vt's br.md ap this territory?
M|Bran|tx|2. Does the tone match the vt's active voice (nz = editorial premium / hb = plain-language trustworthy)?
M|Bran|tx|3. wld the founder feel proud posting this?
M|Bran|tx|If any answer is NO → reframe the pitch, don't submit the off-br version.
M|Stor|it|Each pitch stored in `intelligence_pitches` table
M|Stor|it|CSE fields (signalType, growthHypothesis, scoreBreakdown, cseScore) stored in `full_proposal` jsonb column
M|Stor|it|Pass reasons stored in `pitch_pass_reasons` — ln reads these to avoid re-pitching dismissed territory